### Test Reports Controller Endpoints
### Make sure to replace {{token}} with your actual JWT token

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7175
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get System Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/system-overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Get Ideas Status Distribution
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/ideas/status-distribution
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Get Category Reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get Single Category Report (replace with actual categoryId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/category/YOUR-CATEGORY-ID-HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Get Ideas By Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/ideas/by-date?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Get User Activity Report - FIXED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/users/activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Get Top Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/top-categories?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Get Approval Trends - FIXED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/approval-trends?months=6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Get Employee Contributions - FIXED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/employee-contributions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 10. Get Latest Ideas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/ideas/latest?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. Export Reports to Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/export/excel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

